//  Funtion
// It's is block of code in which we perform multiple task and multiple time also.

// there are four type of funtion 
// which written below
// funtion with return
// funtion with non return
// funtion with parameter
// funtion with non parameter

// Recursion 
// It's is one of the type of the loop in which we will call the funtion recursively.
// there are serveral types of it which is written below.

// Direct Recursion : In this funtion we call funtion directly.
// Indirect Recursion : In this funtion we call indrectly funtion directly. Exp. a calls b calls c calls d calls a.
// Tail Revcursion : In this when we call one last funtion is known as tail recursion.
// Non Tail Recursion : In this when we call funtion again and again it's known as non tail recursion.

// Pointers
// It stores the address of another variable.
// Expl. : - int a = 10; int *ptr = &a;

// where * is showing values.
// where & is showing addresses.
